title: A Note to Delete
text:
OH GOD YOU LOOKED AT IT. NO ONE WAS SUPPOSED TO SEE THIS. YOU'VE DOOMED US ALL. PEACE BE WITH YOU.  HEED MY WARNING:


DON'T LOOK AT THE MOON.

OR DO.

IT'S BEAUTIFUL TONIGHT.

title: A Note to View
text:
What a nice happy note! Please don't look at the other notes. They weren't meant to be seen by human eyes!

Thanks for Stopping By!
